4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to develop skills as cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 participants. Students gain expertise in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with cloud security, penetration testing, and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by multiple institutions. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop